summary: This document is a Voting and Support Agreement dated November 14, 2025, between Xeno Acquisition Corp. and securityholders of Repare Therapeutics Inc., regarding the acquisition of all outstanding shares of the Company. The agreement outlines the obligations of the securityholders to vote in favor of the acquisition and related resolutions, refrain from supporting competing proposals, and not transfer their securities, among other commitments, until the acquisition is completed or the agreement is terminated.
